## 📌 Overview

AzureShield is a production **LLM Safety & Red-Teaming Automation Platform** built for Microsoft's Azure OpenAI Service. It automatically generates thousands of adversarial prompts — jailbreaks, prompt injections, harmful content — tests every model version against them, and blocks unsafe releases before they reach production customers.

**Key Results:**
- ⚡ **94%** reduction in safety incident detection time (days → under 2 hours)
- 🧪 **10,000+** adversarial scenarios generated per model version
- 🚫 **98.7%** of safety regressions caught before production
- 📋 **35%** improvement in Responsible AI policy compliance
- 🏢 Protecting **200+ enterprise Azure OpenAI customers**

