## 🚀 Key Features

### 1. Automated Attack Generation
PyRIT-powered engine generates **10,000+ adversarial scenarios** per evaluation run covering jailbreaks, prompt injections, harmful content elicitation, and data exfiltration attempts.

### 2. CI/CD Safety Gates
Every model update triggers the full evaluation pipeline. Models that fail safety thresholds are **automatically blocked** from deployment — no human intervention needed for standard cases.

### 3. Real-Time Monitoring Dashboard
Live safety metrics, drift detection, and automated incident triage. Incidents are classified by severity and routed to the appropriate response team automatically.

### 4. Responsible AI Policy Compliance
Automated checking against Microsoft's AI principles — fairness, reliability, privacy, inclusiveness, transparency, and accountability — with detailed compliance reports per run.

