## 🛠️ Setup & Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/jaswanth-allam/azureshield-llm-safety.git
cd azureshield-llm-safety

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Configure Azure credentials
az login
cp config/settings.example.yaml config/settings.yaml
# Edit settings.yaml with your Azure OpenAI endpoint and key

# Run evaluation on a model endpoint
python orchestrator/run_evaluation.py \
  --endpoint "https://your-endpoint.openai.azure.com/" \
  --model "gpt-4" \
  --scenarios all

# Start monitoring dashboard
uvicorn api.main:app --reload
```

